# Server-side token used to write sky slices into the data repo
# (Jada-Q/sky-slices-data) as GitHub Issues.
#
# Locally: `gh auth token` returns yours.
#   printf "GITHUB_TOKEN=$(gh auth token)\n" > .env.local
#
# In production (Vercel): generate a fine-grained PAT scoped to
# "sky-slices-data" with `Issues: read & write`, set it as
# GITHUB_TOKEN in the project's environment variables.
GITHUB_TOKEN=
